<body>
    <h1>T9- Requirement Analysis Document</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <h1 local-id=3D"2d6ea05b0466" id=3D"T9-RequirementAnalysisDocument-=
1.Introduction">1. Introduction</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"f30de12081d9" id=3D"T9-RequirementAnalysisDocument-1.1Purpo=
se">1.1 Purpose</h2>
<p local-id=3D"0bcf5ed34d2f">This document defines the requirements for dep=
loying the PowerOfMath application using both Serverless and Traditional VM=
-Based architectures on AWS Cloud.</p>
<p local-id=3D"d6b2cb4be3f5">The purpose of this document is to:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"76f2fc307621">
<li local-id=3D"66871bd18a1c">
<p local-id=3D"c19fa8869cba">Clearly outline project objectives</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fba02fbdeffa">
<p local-id=3D"cd7ba76ad773">Define functional and non-functional requireme=
nts</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"efe62efaa70f">
<p local-id=3D"dce3cb3f9638">Identify constraints and risks</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6d21281bdf7d">
<p local-id=3D"eec373275fc8">Provide a structured implementation blueprint<=
/p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"f2d0ad5d230c"><strong>Intended Audience:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"2e808d7bf5f8">
<li local-id=3D"40d3b0ff3dca">
<p local-id=3D"4ae69beb891d">CTO</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"53608d6e4992">
<p local-id=3D"fb30415ac8b5">Solution Architects</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4430cfea7f2d">
<p local-id=3D"fb0ddde46f01">DevOps Engineers</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8333ba0b1ec4">
<p local-id=3D"468ae297af04">Cloud Engineers</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"677e0e9dfab2">
<p local-id=3D"40083748cacc">Technical Review Panel</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"a8e45d940e80">
<h2 local-id=3D"eb9bc9bdae97" id=3D"T9-RequirementAnalysisDocument-1.2Scope=
">1.2 Scope</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"3f859c6b622c" id=3D"T9-RequirementAnalysisDocument-Included=
inScope">Included in Scope</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"08debd5d28ff">
<li local-id=3D"308012562dc2">
<p local-id=3D"efaafceaa251">Deployment of PowerOfMath application on AWS</=
p></li>
<li local-id=3D"54612d73c3d8">
<p local-id=3D"7d92e63a0e56">Implementation using:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"aa153fe20376">
<li local-id=3D"ae43a948ba7f">
<p local-id=3D"eaaea4ced58a">Serverless Architecture (Lambda + API Gateway =
+ DynamoDB + S3 + CloudFront)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2cc048bc20a4">
<p local-id=3D"2cff4e7857a2">VM-Based Architecture (EC2 + Gunicorn + Nginx)=
</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"38e34bdc4fe7">
<p local-id=3D"d36c38fb3dd7">SSL configuration for both architectures</p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"b79646975eda">
<p local-id=3D"a8cd69e360bb">Public accessibility via HTTPS</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8bf218ed1a14">
<p local-id=3D"42cbef80fa34">Security configuration (IAM, Security Groups, =
Reverse Proxy)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"65b869332722">
<p local-id=3D"2c7d37e5ceff">Documentation and comparison analysis</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"ee5faabc3a51" id=3D"T9-RequirementAnalysisDocument-OutofSco=
pe">Out of Scope</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"8ea7cc456058">
<li local-id=3D"542308229e0a">
<p local-id=3D"df9037252138">CI/CD pipeline implementation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5d1878ed77cb">
<p local-id=3D"5f86294247eb">Infrastructure as Code (Terraform/CDK)</p></li=
>
<li local-id=3D"ffea6d791719">
<p local-id=3D"0b72379bba31">Auto Scaling configuration</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5eea0a320a4a">
<p local-id=3D"dfb95fd06a17">Advanced monitoring dashboards</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"58f0898c0d0c">
<p local-id=3D"4d26ef103767">Production-grade load balancing</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"5e6a186829f5">
<h2 local-id=3D"0ff02ee4b5c1" id=3D"T9-RequirementAnalysisDocument-1.3Defin=
itions,Acronyms,andAbbreviations">1.3 Definitions, Acronyms, and Abbreviati=
ons</h2>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"80=
88b0ea-0a0a-4706-b7f5-7d1b10225e67" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"ea6d2a9c2bee">
<th data-local-id=3D"30bc964fafbc" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"1a0b047dfd3e">Term</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"bb9c3bf9cf89" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"e65c3af17943">Meaning</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"27b17893dbe5">
<td data-local-id=3D"d09088443466" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"9db6680db76d">AWS</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"55498ab3f088" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"ee3f9b9bc58c">Amazon Web Services</p></td>
</tr>
