</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"fb7dd58a64c2">
<td data-local-id=3D"94275dbce16a" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"2f2188912a96">API</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"f286e0fad4a9" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"84423e4b275d">Application Programming Interface</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"186b6ab4e089">
<td data-local-id=3D"a352a5cd91c0" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"3a3505763be0">SSL</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"9e05c2ec9c2f" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"c05f5d4cb89d">Secure Socket Layer</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"e16fbea38662">
<td data-local-id=3D"0d985ffb5fba" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"800ad6824d4f">ACM</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"66d92da88a75" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"12041f2be313">AWS Certificate Manager</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"6cc0c6bd4525">
<td data-local-id=3D"748386e54870" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"612df2f3affd">CDN</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"487ddee77f12" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"6ff56d68ccaf">Content Delivery Network</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"b5d3773df435">
<td data-local-id=3D"637d25039a57" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"82497dc728cb">WSGI</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"08d51c93087c" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"03cee43b5b0e">Web Server Gateway Interface</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"738a4f9ff23a">
<td data-local-id=3D"cf3958946fe7" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"ab84ff45d714">TCO</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"cfb4942ed5e4" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"e550b732cb0f">Total Cost of Ownership</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<hr local-id=3D"3bed774945e7">
<h2 local-id=3D"4f6218a35449" id=3D"T9-RequirementAnalysisDocument-1.4Refer=
ences">1.4 References</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"4133069f5826">
<li local-id=3D"23a05e34a3f3">
<p local-id=3D"31923ded50a6">GitHub Repository: pushkar-iamops/powerofmath<=
/p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3f774795fd5e">
<p local-id=3D"4e7626a36db3">AWS Documentation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f0105183916f">
<p local-id=3D"e51d5a831d9a">Let=E2=80=99s Encrypt Documentation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"201ed2ba7f54">
<p local-id=3D"82c4eab276d8">AWS Well-Architected Framework</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"cb8649b7fef2">
<h2 local-id=3D"1034302e0a69" id=3D"T9-RequirementAnalysisDocument-1.5Overv=
iew">1.5 Overview</h2>
<p local-id=3D"d6f50ead6d52">This document includes:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"9c93322ea7a7">
<li local-id=3D"35cd8b09e57a">
<p local-id=3D"0475ecaf2a3e">Project Overview</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9dc5d9733004">
<p local-id=3D"ec1adb04e693">Functional Requirements</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2b59f48ef881">
<p local-id=3D"b9fbe22ff6fb">Non-Functional Requirements</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ab50fc97fe8b">
<p local-id=3D"c74c3075c0f9">Risk Assessment</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"87313451bb91">
<p local-id=3D"58b72a864c2c">Assumptions and Dependencies</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"6b451f408e58">It serves as a blueprint for structured AWS de=
ployment.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"7ee7c0b5c91d">
<h1 local-id=3D"33d476b66810" id=3D"T9-RequirementAnalysisDocument-2.Projec=
tOverview">2. Project Overview</h1>
<hr local-id=3D"769a2fde3c8a">
<h2 local-id=3D"ac5e6cb6a105" id=3D"T9-RequirementAnalysisDocument-2.1Proje=
ctObjectives">2.1 Project Objectives</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"5b5a9741d61c">
<li local-id=3D"ca888587ee99">
<p local-id=3D"b1c5ee497ddc">Deploy PowerOfMath using Serverless architectu=
re</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d73261638d15">
<p local-id=3D"12eb9a59f6c8">Deploy same application using EC2-based archit=
ecture</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6c0acafe407d">
<p local-id=3D"d11b595790e3">Secure both deployments using HTTPS</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c2016dd49140">
<p local-id=3D"8163e7e15fd8">Compare operational and scaling differences</p=
></li>
<li local-id=3D"6e53b6a65629">
<p local-id=3D"246b6f59f485">Deliver professional-grade documentation</p></=
li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"67c05a45d4d0">
<h2 local-id=3D"a312e6b4a773" id=3D"T9-RequirementAnalysisDocument-2.2Busin=
essGoals">2.2 Business Goals</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"2f7e8006b2ac">
<li local-id=3D"b212a3b8667b">
<p local-id=3D"c52629be559d">Demonstrate cloud architecture flexibility</p>=
</li>
<li local-id=3D"edf2e3ad9c0e">
<p local-id=3D"8cfbb365cffb">Compare cost models (Elastic vs Fixed Compute)=
</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6b12b7a9000a">
<p local-id=3D"0e6d16b4cee6">Implement secure, production-like environment<=
/p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3922e4885237">
<p local-id=3D"497a9af44941">Provide scalable and maintainable solution</p>=
</li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"472682e9ab45">
<h2 local-id=3D"d59475873cf5" id=3D"T9-RequirementAnalysisDocument-2.3Backg=
round">2.3 Background</h2>
<p local-id=3D"76c1d3993035">PowerOfMath is a simple two-tier web applicati=
on:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"1ee71c9050bf">
<li local-id=3D"9df242a53dff">
<p local-id=3D"ae1e9180a876">Frontend: Static HTML interface</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b2f2487122b7">
<p local-id=3D"e3412216bb0d">Backend: Python-based mathematical calculation=
 service</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"ab231d9bfaf1">The project requires showcasing two cloud depl=
oyment strategies:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"84ae19e70729">
<li local-id=3D"4ea2cdd21c9f">
<p local-id=3D"488241ef565b">Managed serverless environment</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1289ececa4fd">
<p local-id=3D"6e876202e1ea">Self-managed virtual machine environment</p></=
li>
</ol>
<hr local-id=3D"62375b275b3f">
<h2 local-id=3D"678962e4c3cc" id=3D"T9-RequirementAnalysisDocument-2.4Const=
raints">2.4 Constraints</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"4e3e394b1a17">
<li local-id=3D"28ee03dd57a5">
<p local-id=3D"4fab9b495917">Time limit: 5 hours</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"529e2067e73a">
<p local-id=3D"7ae787921e3e">Budget: AWS Free Tier preferred</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3abb254facb9">
<p local-id=3D"a928f56e183c">No CI/CD requirement</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3c7d1653c041">
<p local-id=3D"c68ea1d33069">No domain initially available</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e55af8de5866">
<p local-id=3D"8c23567acb24">No enterprise monitoring tools</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"f09cf22efec3">
<h1 local-id=3D"1962ff46cd50" id=3D"T9-RequirementAnalysisDocument-3.Functi=
onalRequirements">3. Functional Requirements</h1>
<hr local-id=3D"3a65598657fc">
<h2 local-id=3D"de9812f1f98e" id=3D"T9-RequirementAnalysisDocument-3.1UseCa=
seDiagram(DescribeinDocumentation)">3.1 Use Case Diagram (Describe in Docum=
entation)</h2>
<p local-id=3D"b3faa15a19af">Actors:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"6279a4ecbd36">
<li local-id=3D"3a255fbac6b4">
<p local-id=3D"67f23e439e39">End User</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c572bd04211d">
<p local-id=3D"d6a65ab8c703">AWS Infrastructure</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"85a65e579819">
<p local-id=3D"1fdc05e3a7e1">DevOps Engineer</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"8663358c81ef">Use Cases:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"7d8fa7b9697a">
<li local-id=3D"728efbe169ee">
<p local-id=3D"b6556f25ca3a">Access Application</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f2fa0dcf2493">
<p local-id=3D"6dd81220d0c7">Submit Calculation Request</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"83700698eb63">
<p local-id=3D"9b0a9326dcf1">Process Backend Logic</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5f7d3babeb13">
<p local-id=3D"6f9ba56474f7">Store Data in Database</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"77b325351695">
<p local-id=3D"d8f9d74f578f">Secure Application via HTTPS</p></li>
</ul><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper c=
onfluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image ima=
