<h2 local-id=3D"7dc090a98fad" id=3D"T9-RequirementAnalysisDocument-3.2UseCa=
ses">3.2 Use Cases</h2>
<hr local-id=3D"be9d74a9cbb6">
<h3 local-id=3D"eb0a64b698aa" id=3D"T9-RequirementAnalysisDocument-3.2.1Use=
Case1:PerformMathematicalCalculation">3.2.1 Use Case 1: Perform Mathematica=
l Calculation</h3>
<p local-id=3D"22df69e48372">Description:<br>
User submits base and exponent values and receives calculated result.</p>
<p local-id=3D"d34c4676f3ba">Actors:<br>
End User</p>
<p local-id=3D"c439bf0a5ea4">Preconditions:<br>
Application must be publicly accessible</p>
<p local-id=3D"968364714c6c">Postconditions:<br>
Calculation result displayed to user</p>
<p local-id=3D"6446686eec76">Flow of Events:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"e6bb956f8faf">
<li local-id=3D"892ad7fa9a9c">
<p local-id=3D"5b544ae658a9">User opens application URL</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"57da74eca695">
<p local-id=3D"ec17e46be5b6">User enters base and exponent</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f35cd2e2a4e6">
<p local-id=3D"6bcbf3d38290">Frontend sends POST request to backend</p></li=
>
<li local-id=3D"06a6706353f8">
<p local-id=3D"d5f190dc1e4e">Backend computes result</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"92f27c7c6bea">
<p local-id=3D"bbd46651d9cb">Result stored in database</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fbcb55116c1f">
<p local-id=3D"e2e8dac15bc9">Result returned to user</p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"9ca685be6bde">Alternative Flows:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"f66e304a8181">
<li local-id=3D"012842d2c8fc">
<p local-id=3D"6157932b9c26">Invalid input =E2=86=92 Error returned</p></li=
>
<li local-id=3D"23652e906d65">
<p local-id=3D"d95ff5c28d48">Backend failure =E2=86=92 HTTP error response<=
/p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"9058a3f9455a">
<h3 local-id=3D"6fd9f0419986" id=3D"T9-RequirementAnalysisDocument-3.2.2Use=
Case2:SecureApplicationAccess">3.2.2 Use Case 2: Secure Application Access<=
/h3>
<p local-id=3D"4a86fa88e2d4">Description:<br>
Ensure all traffic is encrypted using HTTPS.</p>
<p local-id=3D"4228fad13d11">Actors:<br>
End User</p>
<p local-id=3D"4f08664974ce">Preconditions:<br>
SSL certificate configured</p>
<p local-id=3D"55ad53e33d98">Postconditions:<br>
Secure HTTPS connection established</p>
<p local-id=3D"1b3cba70c266">Flow:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"34a5b7b5900a">
<li local-id=3D"e4be72c912ec">
<p local-id=3D"ce00f071ee52">User accesses domain</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"02a01c28201a">
<p local-id=3D"252c5c28467c">SSL handshake occurs</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7efabcf7d5c1">
<p local-id=3D"b3bdfc7f5225">Secure communication established</p></li>
</ol>
<hr local-id=3D"6f7ef2e21ac7">
<h1 local-id=3D"7682f638f46b" id=3D"T9-RequirementAnalysisDocument-4.Non-Fu=
nctionalRequirements">4. Non-Functional Requirements</h1>
<hr local-id=3D"8a3e9276ecc4">
<h2 local-id=3D"8933593ef8a6" id=3D"T9-RequirementAnalysisDocument-4.1Perfo=
rmanceRequirements">4.1 Performance Requirements</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"b179c1d88079">
<li local-id=3D"c6069a8af5f7">
<p local-id=3D"ee62f4642812">Response time under 2 seconds</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"05d0ea9e2ec0">
<p local-id=3D"885730322fcb">Handle concurrent user requests</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"99a9f16e0b83">
<p local-id=3D"d1ba67d4e613">No backend port exposure</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"9e757a83e6e0">
<h2 local-id=3D"ef5621ac5725" id=3D"T9-RequirementAnalysisDocument-4.2Secur=
ityRequirements">4.2 Security Requirements</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"83d08059b071">
<li local-id=3D"24c5857c86fb">
<p local-id=3D"7b91725d794e">HTTPS enforced</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2692010d17f2">
<p local-id=3D"972234a51a48">IAM least privilege principle</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b718de56510f">
<p local-id=3D"0f259e8f8f11">Security Group restrictions</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e328102fb073">
<p local-id=3D"f8930d73cfbb">Backend isolation via reverse proxy</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"86229e3231ea">
<p local-id=3D"ec01988cd2a4">No hardcoded credentials</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"8024f3134f9e">
<h2 local-id=3D"86c683c1fbb0" id=3D"T9-RequirementAnalysisDocument-4.3Usabi=
lityRequirements">4.3 Usability Requirements</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"81c192431a88">
<li local-id=3D"d255aed570ad">
<p local-id=3D"0ae830ae0842">Simple UI</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c188c048b892">
<p local-id=3D"485ce8ccdcd6">Clear input fields</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b29f97446b7b">
<p local-id=3D"e66420707cb2">Immediate result display</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"57a810eed62d">
<p local-id=3D"cbc7bdd4cbdc">Browser-compatible design</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"b692b7fceee4">
<h2 local-id=3D"726b24ca24a8" id=3D"T9-RequirementAnalysisDocument-4.4Relia=
bilityRequirements">4.4 Reliability Requirements</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"78ac05d19031">
<li local-id=3D"0559b8b3421b">
<p local-id=3D"d3d31590e5b7">Service restart persistence via systemd</p></l=
i>
<li local-id=3D"bb049a870a30">
<p local-id=3D"314d161e7de1">SSL auto-renewal</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e43cf8425538">
<p local-id=3D"ec3e6a7a3575">Cloud-managed service reliability (Lambda)</p>=
</li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"2e3886a37bf4">
<h2 local-id=3D"bc8ac413d0d7" id=3D"T9-RequirementAnalysisDocument-4.5Compl=
ianceRequirements">4.5 Compliance Requirements</h2>
<p local-id=3D"cc659d41905e">Although no formal compliance framework was re=
quired, best practices were followed:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"88705cbad68f">
<li local-id=3D"0bd546dc0c72">
<p local-id=3D"0a5cad4a771b">Encrypted communication</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8d3c88d94bda">
<p local-id=3D"4ee8a6083037">Controlled access policies</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"cdcf407e9d62">
<p local-id=3D"9dfa9f4607a4">Minimal exposed surface area</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"d480c4a92b8d">
<h1 local-id=3D"7ac935fbacab" id=3D"T9-RequirementAnalysisDocument-5.Assump=
tionsandDependencies">5. Assumptions and Dependencies</h1>
<hr local-id=3D"e3b6e0375ddf">
<h2 local-id=3D"c566447fa1cc" id=3D"T9-RequirementAnalysisDocument-5.1Assum=
ptions">5.1 Assumptions</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"3920ee78c25f">
<li local-id=3D"77e6bc98d04c">
<p local-id=3D"fe81174b7318">AWS Free Tier availability</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e41fbaba79a8">
<p local-id=3D"fbcac14301d6">Stable internet connectivity</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f45a41ca8ef1">
<p local-id=3D"740fd74a999b">Domain access for SSL</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"96978a20f096">
<p local-id=3D"a7e93e769c96">IAM permissions available</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"8983a994573c">
<h2 local-id=3D"b345194abf48" id=3D"T9-RequirementAnalysisDocument-5.2Depen=
dencies">5.2 Dependencies</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"fcb5b355638d">
<li local-id=3D"b9a482839743">
<p local-id=3D"96a513ff09e6">AWS Cloud Services</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1318b0bc0be3">
<p local-id=3D"5abcf06e8ee7">GitHub repository</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"05d71dcbe9a7">
<p local-id=3D"e142f197be36">Let=E2=80=99s Encrypt servers</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1f05d871e90b">
<p local-id=3D"88eab6ea084c">DNS configuration support</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"e1fe52758c47">
<h1 local-id=3D"0dd177e0e1c6" id=3D"T9-RequirementAnalysisDocument-6.RiskAn=
alysis">6. Risk Analysis</h1>
<hr local-id=3D"2093efd22637">
<h2 local-id=3D"33e1490d346b" id=3D"T9-RequirementAnalysisDocument-6.1RiskI=
dentification">6.1 Risk Identification</h2>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"84=
ebcc2d-553b-4f9e-888a-920604d5a586" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"d2f9d97cde28">
<th data-local-id=3D"07e31599baad" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"9004b2336c96">Risk</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"1a22037ca9c1" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"951c4ca3b34a">Impact</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"f967a76596cd">
<td data-local-id=3D"942cff2bfdd9" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"9bf7c9ea52aa">DNS propagation delay</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"c86e0f08b3c4" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"b02083206cf4">SSL validation delay</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"9ee91de3550b">
<td data-local-id=3D"9db6e06bf974" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"245864bcf221">Misconfigured IAM role</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"991e1840c368" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"98efa28252cf">Lambda failure</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"464ff79137b2">
<td data-local-id=3D"cbf5bedd65e8" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"43f783861571">Incorrect Nginx config</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"25747bc97d88" class=3D"confluenceTd">
