</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"b93c748f2272">
<td data-local-id=3D"913ab6cc5a00" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"01e86fa3726b">SSL certificate expiry</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"7129d327ef29" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"71f7f5acab2a">Service disruption</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<hr local-id=3D"8ca4e38ab93b">
<h2 local-id=3D"20224dac03c2" id=3D"T9-RequirementAnalysisDocument-6.2RiskM=
itigation">6.2 Risk Mitigation</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"1ceced58a93c">
<li local-id=3D"6fa8a72ec65a">
<p local-id=3D"d4d538b2c174">Validate IAM roles before deployment</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"57d249f510fe">
<p local-id=3D"c1c9b4f780a1">Test API endpoints manually</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"735f9446f7c6">
<p local-id=3D"c06f731d4109">Use nginx -t before restart</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f969afd90e8f">
<p local-id=3D"054379757d4f">Enable auto-renew for SSL certificates</p></li=
>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"4ca87f55d232">
<h1 local-id=3D"12bcf089c63a" id=3D"T9-RequirementAnalysisDocument-7.Glossa=
ry">7. Glossary</h1>
<ul local-id=3D"bc7abbca8bb0">
<li local-id=3D"ccdec3216172">
<p local-id=3D"992ffc1f8ae5">Serverless Architecture: Cloud model without s=
erver management</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9f3a09b0afa2">
<p local-id=3D"32db159297cb">Reverse Proxy: Nginx routing traffic to backen=
d</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5632a08af43e">
<p local-id=3D"66401102c248">Gunicorn: Python WSGI HTTP Server</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"456e6c648636">
<p local-id=3D"cf2329ef43b4">CloudFront: AWS CDN</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"4d3101102f57">
<h1 local-id=3D"6e247b7cfb50" id=3D"T9-RequirementAnalysisDocument-8.Append=
ices">8. Appendices</h1>
